    Modifier and Type
    Class
    Description
    class 
    BorderCache<T extends Region<T>>
    There should be no need for end-users of MesaKit to use BorderCache objects since they are an implementation detail of different Regions to provide containment testing via contains(Location), as well as other such tests.
    static class 
    BorderCache.Settings<R extends Region<R>>
     
    class 
    RegionIdentityCache<T extends Region<T>>
    Holds a set of region identities for a given region type, so they can be quickly loaded, creating a region object for each identity, without loading the borders (either from PBF or Kryo) to find the identities.
